    S "fresh cookies too"
    R "Ahem! in any case, yes we're looking for a sub-in guest, but we’ve got quite a few episodes out already and i gotta say, they’re pretty good."
    C "And it feels good to create, I never thought we’d come this far"

    menu:
        "That's pretty awesome, I want to more about this podcast.":
